rules.ruleString: Incompatible with achievement in (I/W) {ETC4420, ETC5420, ETF3600}
For COURSE_CODE NOT IN {3816, 3822, 4412} Do Must have passed 1 (I/W) units in {ETF2100, ETF5910, ETF9100} with grades other than {STANDARD-DEF, STANDARD-NS} Otherwise true

description: The topics covered in this unit include: Review of regression analysis, Binomial dependent variables, Unordered multinomial dependent variables, Ordered multinomial dependent variables, Duration dependent variable. Computer software EViews will be used to apply these techniques to real world problems.
